spec_data.Name: libspatialite
spec_data.Description:
SpatiaLite is a a library extending the basic SQLite core
in order to get a full fledged Spatial DBMS, really simple
and lightweight, but mostly OGC-SFS compliant.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 04 Aug 2017 01:51:32 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Enables SQLite to support spatial data
